WomanUsesMuayThaiToFightOffPurseSnatcher.summary: Every woman should train in real Muay Thai for self-defense. This woman is defending herself against a man trying to steal her purse. She’s doing everything right—strong in the clinch, breaking it with uppercuts and elbows, then creating distance. Her middle kicks are perfectly timed. What really stands out is her body control and postural awareness—skills you can only develop through consistent training.
